(99,	1,	'2018-11-02 03:04:41',	'2018-11-02 03:04:41',	'With a mission to change a culture and end a brutal tradition, Jaha Dukureh vows, ‘My daughter will not\r\ngo through this. It stops with me’. Jaha’s Promise, follows the life of Jaha Dukureh.\r\nA staggering 200 million women worldwide live with the effects of female genital mutilation (FGM). On average over 6,000 girls are mutilated every day worldwide. A survivor of FGM herself, we watch as Jaha returns to her home country to lead a campaign against FGM. Through her relentless struggle and irrepressible spirit comes a stunning victory. Inspiring all those who hear her story that one woman can really change the world.',	'JAHA’S PROMISE',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'a-woman-captured-sydney-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy',	'',	'',	'2018-11-02 04:02:25',	'2018-11-02 04:02:25',	'',	0,	'http://localhost:3157/ruby/?event=a-woman-captured-sydney-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy-copy',	0,	'event',	'',	0),
