(170,	1,	'2018-11-02 04:53:48',	'2018-11-02 04:53:48',	'Celebrating a milestone 10th Anniversary, the Human Rights Arts &amp; Film Festival is back for 2017 with an exciting new selection of international and locally made films, vibrant arts program and topical forums.\r\n\r\nThe full program will be released 4th April, but while you wait in anticipation for the grand reveal, six sessions will be available for purchase for a limited time only until midnight Monday 6th March.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://2018.hraff.org.au/\">PURCHASE PRE-RELEASE TICKETS HERE</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFestival and National Tour dates for 2017:\r\n\r\nMELBOURNE 4 — 18 MAY 2017\r\n\r\nSYDNEY 23 – 27 MAY\r\n\r\nCANBERRA 29 – 31 MAY\r\n\r\nPERTH 29 – 31 MAY\r\n\r\nBRISBANE 1 – 3 JUNE\r\n\r\nWe look forward to seeing you at the event!',	'SELECT 2017 10TH ANNIVERSARY FESTIVAL SESSIONS AVAILABLE UNTIL MONDAY!',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'select-2017-10th-anniversary-festival-sessions-available-until-monday',	'',	'',	'2018-11-02 04:57:12',	'2018-11-02 04:57:12',	'',	0,	'http://localhost:3157/ruby/?p=170',	0,	'post',	'',	0),
